@startuml
' Embedded standalone style block (replicated per file; standalone)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor White
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam nodesep 50
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam padding 3
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

left to right direction

actor "Usuario\n(Administrador /\nPersonal Logistico /\nCliente)" as Usuario
boundary "GraphQL endpoint\n(AuthService / auth.context)" as Boundary
control "AuthService.Login\n(auth_service.go)" as Control
entity "User\n(users.go)" as Entity
database "NeonDB\n(PostgreSQL)" as DB

Usuario --> Boundary : 1: ingresar credenciales
Boundary --> Control : 2: mutation login(email, password)
Control --> Entity : 3: buscar usuario por correo
Entity --> DB : 4: SELECT users WHERE email
DB --> Entity : 5: fila de usuario
Entity --> Control : 6: User(IsActive, hash, role)
Control --> Control : 7: bcrypt VerifyPassword + emitir JWT RS256
Control --> Boundary : 8: token JWT + rol (o error 401 / user is inactive)
Boundary --> Usuario : 9: acceso concedido o error
@enduml
